{"id": 2424, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都遇过哪些信息分享难题？", "description": "世界上最遥远的距离，是想用蓝牙传张照片，却发现你用苹果我用安卓。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 5992, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180625180919dIGAf20WT8JjZsN5.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4394, "title": "现如今你都遇过哪些信息分享难题？", "content": "社交网络上你都遇过哪些信息分享难题？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 287365, "content": "微信文章里不能直接分享文字，要手动退出复制粘贴", "image": "img/option/option/201806251649288pyH3SmzlIO9ArGV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287380, "content": "转发分享时有勾选陷阱，一不小心就关注了啥营销号", "image": "img/option/option/20180625170743vFfARbwgQ2TiNtIP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287381, "content": "国外社交软件\"分享至微信/微博\"的按钮，按了也没反应", "image": "img/option/option/20180625172246mWd03DuThMa1Acob.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287382, "content": "转发文件图片必须先加载，一段时间没点开的会过期", "image": "img/option/option/20180625171348fj4FJv8DTdqL7anZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287383, "content": "朋友圈发视频必须是MP4，10秒以内，宽高比不超过2", "image": "img/option/option/201806251719176sS9DdpgzbKZkqr1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287388, "content": "airdrop能不能连上全靠命", "image": "img/option/option/20180625172904esuUD1Io5HhV2d9P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287391, "content": "抖音淘宝在微信受限，分享要先下载图片视频再上传", "image": "img/option/option/20180625172644cBlsoTZEYDHXWmG4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 289150, "content": "安卓和苹果手机之间的蓝牙互不相认", "image": "img/option/option/20180625173244Gve3wCWHmFSgrKTn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}